snippet.title: Freddy Fazbear's Pizzeria Simulator - Coming to Switch and Xbox Oct 31st
snippet.description:
- Please subscribe to our channel -

Freddy Fazbear's Pizzeria** Simulator is coming to Switch and Xbox Oct 31st, 2020. The PS4 version will be coming soon after. Please prepare your business plan in advance to assure safe and profitable operation of your own Freddy Fazbear's Pizzeria store.

**Fazbear Entertainment cannot be held responsible for the disappearances, deaths or mutilations that may occur as a result of operating the Freddy Fazbear's Pizzeria franchise.

#MadeWithFusion #FNAF
